Empress star Terrence Howard and his wife Mira Pak Howard on Wednesday visited Uganda. Terrence is an American actor who has starred in the Empire TV series as Lucious Lyon. They are reportedly in Uganda following the invitation of  Uganda’s Minister for Agriculture, Animal Industry and Fisheries, Frank Tumwebaze. During their tour, they met with President Yoweri Museveni, in the State House in Kampala. The couple also visited Buganda Road crafts village. Terrence and Mira pledged to be great ambassadors for the #ExploreUganda brand on return.